        "title": "Feedback and Reflection",
        "content": "After each round:\n\n*   **Feedback:** The speaker provides feedback to the listener on their active listening skills.\n    *   Was the listener attentive?\n    *   Did they understand the message?\n    *   What could they improve?\n*   **Reflection:** Consider what you learned about your own listening habits and areas for improvement."
      }
